bayou.html

Class HtmlRaw

  • java.lang.Object
    • bayou.html.HtmlRaw
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HtmlPiece

    public class HtmlRaw
extends Object
implements HtmlPiece
    Html raw content.

    The content will be rendered verbatim, without any escaping.

    For example, `new HtmlRaw("<td>", 1, "</td>")` will be rendered as "<td>1</td>".
